WEBVTT


00:00:00.021 --> 00:00:01.900
Big news. Italy, Slovenia

00:00:01.901 --> 00:00:04.518
and Croatia are teaming up to stop a legal migration.

00:00:04.541 --> 00:00:05.900
The Croatian Prime Minister

00:00:05.901 --> 00:00:06.860
Andre Plankovich

00:00:06.861 --> 00:00:08.820
has announced that 7000 police officers

00:00:08.821 --> 00:00:10.500
will be deployed to secure the border

00:00:10.501 --> 00:00:12.638
and new surveillance technology will be installed

00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:13.953
detect groups of migrants

00:00:13.954 --> 00:00:15.585
trying to illegally enter Croatia.

00:00:15.994 --> 00:00:18.225
It's a bold move to tackle the issue head on.

00:00:18.274 --> 00:00:19.585
What do you think about this
